episodes.name: Courtyards Reveal
episodes.overview: A body corporate meeting is called and we know what that means - trouble. The teams race to reveal their courtyards. Will the judges be blown away? Who will take home the $10,000 cash?

episodes.name: Studios Begin
episodes.overview: It’s studio week and our couples receive some exciting news from Scotty. There is another body corporate meeting, which is the meeting to end all meetings.

episodes.name: Studios Continue
episodes.overview: The fallout from the body corporate is massive as two teams go to war. A heartfelt challenge takes place, with $5000 up for grabs.

episodes.overview: One teams fall from grace sends shockwaves through The Block.

episodes.overview: A fishing challenge with a prize worth over $100,000 brings out the competitive spirit in our Blockheads.

episodes.name: Guest Bedroom 2 Reveal
episodes.overview: Keith is back, Grant actually enjoys his birthday and Jesse and Paige are not happy. Find out if Kylie and Brad use the penguin to nab the win in the second Guest Bedroom?

episodes.name: Main Bedroom & WIR Week (1)
episodes.overview: One of the most dramatic episodes sees one team leave The Block under extreme circumstances. The other contestants are left shaken and wondering who the new competition will be.

episodes.name: Main Bedroom & WIR Week (2)
episodes.overview: Two new Blockheads arrive at the island, but the red carpet is not exactly rolled out. Scotty is less than impressed when Grant decides he can make the rules up as he goes along.

episodes.name: Main Bedroom & WIR Week (3)
episodes.overview: The youngest Block contestants ever are off to a rocky start and it's all aboard the party bus for a challenge.

episodes.name: Main Bedroom and WIR Reveal
episodes.overview: The Blockheads are not in a sharing mood, which causes the new team to struggle. This week's room judging sees one team take out $10,000 for their innovative design.

episodes.name: Kitchen Week (1)
episodes.overview: The Blockheads kick off kitchen week with an amazing community-based challenge. Foreman Dan and Grant come to blows.

episodes.name: Kitchen Week (2)
episodes.overview: The new kids on The Block and their builders decide to part ways, their potential new builders causes angst amongst the other teams.

episodes.name: Kitchen Week (3)
episodes.overview: The Blockheads that win the community challenge are loud and proud. And Shelley is immortalised by the quirky Ricky and Haydn.

episodes.name: Kitchen Reveal
episodes.overview: The Blockheads' show stopping kitchens are judged and Scotty makes a game changing announcement that will turn auction day on its head.

episodes.name: Guest Ensuite Week (1)
episodes.overview: It's hump week on The Block, and the contestants are feeling it, with both Mimi and Courtney struggling with design block as they try to come up with ideas for their Guest Ensuites.

episodes.name: Guest Ensuite Week (2)
episodes.overview: Rumours that one team haven't been paying their trades see a body corporate called, and tempers frayed.

episodes.name: Guest Ensuite Week (3)
episodes.overview: The Blockheads choose which spaces they will renovate in clubhouse week and Charlotte does a bit snooping on the other team's bathrooms, which does not go down well.

episodes.name: Guest Ensuite Reveal
episodes.overview: Hayden uncovers some videos about Maddy and Charlotte, and a challenge earns one team some much-needed cash. Find out who takes home the $10,000 and who is salty about it.

episodes.name: Living Dining Week (1)
episodes.overview: The teams start designing their living/dining spaces. Maddy and Charlotte fangirl over Eliza and Liberty.

episodes.name: Living Dining Week (2)
episodes.overview: Kristian is forced to go cap in hand to Maddy and Charlotte, but who will be the bigger person?

episodes.name: Living Dining Week (3)
episodes.overview: The actions of House 2 have far-reaching consequences for their fellow contestants.

episodes.name: Living Dining Reveal
episodes.overview: The judges are impressed by the Blockheads' stylish living and dining rooms. Find out who takes home a much-needed $10,000.

episodes.name: Office Rumpus Week (1)
episodes.overview: The Blockheads are in for a massive week with office, rumpus and hallways to design, and if that wasn't enough, Scotty throws a challenge into the mix.

episodes.name: Office Rumpus Week (2)
episodes.overview: The teams must get their homes ready for 100 potential buyers and the opportunity to win $50,000.

episodes.name: Office Rumpus Week (3)
episodes.overview: The buyers' jury winner is announced, making one team $50,000 richer, and most contestants are struggling to get all their spaces ready for judging.

episodes.name: Office Rumpus Reveal
episodes.overview: The Blockheads all have a different take on their office and rumpus areas. Which teams' spaces impress the judges?

episodes.name: Guest Bedroom & Laundry Week (1)
episodes.overview: Some blockheads are upset after last night's judging. Will they get their groove back as they work on another guest bedroom and laundry?

episodes.name: Guest Bedroom & Laundry Week (2)
episodes.overview: The Blockheads are elevated when their families come to visit, and they create a fun carnival challenge on Phillip Island.

episodes.name: Guest Bedroom & Laundry Week (3)
episodes.overview: The contestants are hard at work creating the last rooms on the inside of their homes.

episodes.name: Guest Bedroom & Laundry Reveal
episodes.overview: It's a race to the finish as The Blockheads push to deliver the final internal spaces of their homes. Find out who takes out $10,000 in judging.

episodes.name: Backyard Week (1)
episodes.overview: The teams tackle the enormous task of landscaping their backyards. The contestant's chumps dinner serves up an unpleasant atmosphere.

episodes.name: Backyard Week (2)
episodes.overview: There is mayhem on site as the contestants and their landscapers battle to create their extensive backyards.

episodes.name: Backyard Week (3)
episodes.overview: House Five's landscaper is getting attention for all the wrong reasons, and all the Blockheads are under pressure as they try to create stunning backyards.

episodes.name: Backyard Week Reveal
episodes.overview: The teams race to finish their backyards. Who takes home the $10,000?

episodes.name: Front Yard Week (1)
episodes.overview: Fractured relationships see one contestant leave the Block. But the show must go on as there are front yards to finish.

episodes.name: Front Yard Week (2)
episodes.overview: Ricky and Haydn are rocked by a misplaced delivery. Scotty checks how the Blockheads are coping after the exit of their fellow contestant.

episodes.name: Front Yard Week (3)
episodes.overview: The delivery of Ricky and Haydn's massive palm tree causes mayhem for House 4, and they are not happy.

episodes.name: Front Yard Reveal
episodes.overview: One couple is ecstatic to win a car for their front yard, whilst another team member is furious.

episodes.name: Clubhouse Week (1)
episodes.overview: Scotty's HQ transforms into a day spa, cinema, alfresco area, games room and BBQ area.

episodes.overview: Scotty tells one team and their all-star helpers that they must stop spending, and it all gets too much for Mimi.

episodes.name: Clubhouse Reveal
episodes.overview: Find out which team gets $50,000 off their reserve price for creating the most amazing clubhouse space.
